OL,6,FA man has been found guilty of 12
OL,7,Fsexual offences against a child at
OL,8,FJersey's Royal Court.
OL,10,FThe crimes of Richard Louis Romeril,
OL,11,F49, included attempted attempted rape,
OL,12,Fsexual touching, and indecent assault,
OL,13,Fcommitted between March 2011 and March
OL,14,F2022.
OL,16,FDuring a seven-day trial, the court
OL,17,Fheard how the abuse happened almost
OL,18,Fweekly, progressively getting worse
OL,19,Fover time.
